## 2.5 Real-World Engineering Applications

| Domain | Use of Returning Objects |
|---|---|
| **JDBC** | `DriverManager.getConnection()` returns a `Connection` object. |
| **Collections Framework** | `Collections.unmodifiableList()` returns a wrapped, read-only list. |
| **Stream API** | `stream.filter(...).map(...).collect(...)` тАФ every stage returns an object. |
| **Builder Pattern** | `StringBuilder.append()` returns the builder itself to enable chaining. |
| **Date/Time API** | `LocalDate.now()` returns a new `LocalDate` object. |
| **HTTP Networking** | `HttpClient.send()` returns an `HttpResponse<String>` object. |

