### Question B (14 Marks) тАФ [KTU University Exam тАУ Dec 2023] (Alternative Choice)

**(a)** What is method overriding? Write a Java program to demonstrate how `super.method()` is used to call the overridden parent method from within the sub class. *(7 Marks)*

