## 1.5 Why Event Handling Matters in Swings

Swing components (lightweight, 100% Java, pluggable Look & Feel) **do not contain any native OS event-handling code**. They rely entirely on Java's event model. Without event handling, a Swing GUI would be a beautiful but **dead** picture тАФ no buttons could be clicked, no text could be typed.

