|  |  |  |  Layered Pane            |  |  |  |
|  |  |  |  +--------------------+  |  |  |  |
|  |  |  |  |  Content Pane      |  |  |  |  <-- You add components HERE
|  |  |  |  |  (default:         |  |  |  |
|  |  |  |  |  BorderLayout)     |  |  |  |
|  |  |  |  +--------------------+  |  |  |
|  |  |  |  +--------------------+  |  |  |
|  |  |  |  |  Menu Bar (optional)|  |  |  |
