> [!WARNING]
> **Common Student Mistake**: Calling `add()` directly on a `JFrame` from JDK 5+ is technically still allowed (it delegates to the content pane) but is considered **bad practice** in KTU board evaluation. Always use `getContentPane().add()` or set the content pane explicitly.

