**(a) [7 Marks]** Write a Java Swing program to create a JFrame with a JButton labeled "Click Me". Each time the button is clicked, the JLabel text should alternate between "ON" and "OFF". Implement using `ActionListener`.

**(b) [7 Marks]** Compare and contrast `setSize()` and `pack()` methods of JFrame. In what scenarios would you prefer one over the other? Provide code examples.

