> [!TIP]
> **Best practice:** Use `JTextField.LEADING` and `JTextField.TRAILING` instead of `LEFT`/`RIGHT` to support Right-to-Left (RTL) languages like Arabic and Hebrew тАФ a point KTU may give as a 1-mark extra.

