- Abstract declaration + reasoning тЖТ 2 marks
- Fields (`payerName`, `amount`, `timestamp`) with `protected` access тЖТ 1 mark
- Constructor with `super()` chaining readiness тЖТ 1 mark
- `final` `validate()` method with both checks тЖТ 2 marks
- Abstract `processPayment()` declaration тЖТ 1 mark

